      "description": "Magellan IMACS spectroscopic redshift survey of the Bullet Cluster field. ~100 confirmed cluster member galaxies at z~0.296. Velocity dispersion σ_v ~ 1200 km/s. Two distinct velocity components (the two sub-clusters). Collision velocity ~3500 km/s in the plane of the sky (from X-ray bow shock). Spectroscopic confirmation that we are observing a genuine collision event, not a projection. In BEC model: the two velocity components are the two BEC cavities whose interference we observe.",
